It's necessary to install the packages openconnect (handles communication with the VPN
server) and vpnc-script (configure routing and DNS).
# sudo apt-get install openconnect vpnc-scripts
Connecting
# sudo openconnect -b vpn.epfl.ch
Insert the username and password GASPAR .
Option -b allows you to run the VPN in the background.
Disconnecting
# sudo pkill openconnect